OL,3,CFirst look at plans to overhaul Jersey
OL,4,CAirport's departure hall
OL,6,FThe first designs have been released
OL,7,Fto show what Jersey Airport's new
OL,8,Fdeparture hall could look like.
OL,10,FPorts of Jersey says the project will
OL,11,Fgive passengers a more comfortable
OL,12,Fwaiting area ahead of their flights,
OL,13,Fwith more local features, softer
OL,14,Flighting and extra seating.
OL,16,FIt adds that the plans have been
OL,17,Fcreated in partnership with a range of
OL,18,Flocal groups, including Durrell, the
OL,19,FNational Trust and Visit Jersey,
OL,20,Falongside public feedback.
