OL,3,CFirst look at plans to overhaul Jersey
OL,4,CAirport's departure hall
OL,6,F"This project is about creating a
OL,7,Fspace that feels relaxed, functional
OL,8,Fand unmistakably Jersey," Matt Thomas,
OL,9,FPorts' Chief Executive Officer,
OL,10,Fexplains.
OL,12,F"We are really grateful to the wide
OL,13,Fgroup of stakeholders who have kindly
OL,14,Fgiven their time to create a design
OL,15,Fthat celebrates our island."
OL,17,FFiona Brennan from the charity
OL,18,FBrighter Futures adds: "Ports of
OL,19,FJersey listened to our families,
OL,20,Finvolved us in the design process, and
OL,21,Ftook their ideas seriously.
