OL,3,CFirst look at plans to overhaul Jersey
OL,4,CAirport's departure hall
OL,6,F"Often with large projects, people can
OL,7,Ffeel that things are done to them,
OL,8,Frather than with them. This has been
OL,9,Fdifferent."
OL,11,FThe redevelopment started in
OL,12,FSeptember, with early work focused on
OL,13,Frelocating seating areas, removing
OL,14,Folder infrastructure and setting up a
OL,15,Ftemporary cafe and bar to make way for
OL,16,Fthe changes.
