OL,3,CFirst look at plans to overhaul Jersey
OL,4,CAirport's departure hall
OL,6,FPorts says the new departure hall will
OL,7,Fsee expanded dining and retail
OL,8,Foptions, a mezzanine level with free
OL,9,Frunway views, and quiet and family
OL,10,Fzones.
OL,12,FGrass-like carpets and sand coloured
OL,13,Fwalkways are meant to reflect the
OL,14,Fisland's coastal paths, while timber
OL,15,Fcolumns and local plants portray
OL,16,FJersey's woodland.
OL,18,FThe first phase is expected to be
OL,19,Fcompleted by summer 2026, with the
OL,20,Ffull new departure lounge ready by
OL,21,Fsummer 2027.
